Paper: hep-th/0210199

Date: 2002-10-21

Title: Representation of small conformal algebra

Authors: D.M. Belov

Comments: 12 pages, LaTeX 2e

In hep-th/0202087 it was argued that the operator L_0 is bad defined inkappa-basis as a kernel operator. Indeed, we show that L_0 is a differenceoperator. We also find a representation of L_1 and L_{-1} in a class ofdifference operators.